snippet.title: Steven Universe Mash-Up
snippet.description: Steven enters the Minecraft universe in this Diamond-worthy Mash-Up! Contains Steven Universe-themed skins, textures, original music from the show, and all your favourite locations, from Beach City to Homeworld. Believe in Steven!
